data.description:
SELLER OFFERING $10k towards Buyer's Closing Costs/Rate Buy down fee upon successful COE.  Beautiful single-level home features vaulted ceilings and an open feel. This split floor plan has 4 bedrooms and 2 bath.  Greatroom has plenty of space, entertainment niche. Kitchen is setup for the chef with staggered cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, center island w/breakfast bar and dining.
The master bedroom, tub/shower, double sink vanity and large walk in closet.   Outside you will find a covered patio, grassy area, raised paver patio with gas firepit and seating.  Side gate offers easy access to the back yard. 2 car garage w/cabinets.
